author: COMSOL
description: A way to study coupled macroscale and microscale mass balances in 1D models of reactors packed with catalyst is to use several geometries. The model requires two geometries, one for each system scale, to compute the reacting species concentration profiles along the packed bed reactor as well as within catalyst pellets.
label: packed_bed_reactor.mph
